921" end="00:45.178">the</span> <span begin="00:45.178" end="00:46.026">sweat</span> <span begin="00:46.026" end="00:47.181">that</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">寒意浸透冷汗</span></p><p begin="00:48.072" end="00:49.997" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:48.072" end="00:48.362">You'll</span> <span begin="00:48.362" end="00:48.762">waste</span> <span begin="00:48.762" end="00:49.237">a</span><span begin="00:49.237" end="00:49.997">way</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">终将枯竭消亡</span></p><p begin="00:52.323" end="00:56.051" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:52.323" end="00:52.478">And</span> <span begin="00:52.478" end="00:52.674">you</span> <span begin="00:52.674" end="00:53.124">car</span><span begin="00:53.124" end="00:53.549">ry</span> <span begin="00:53.549" end="00:53.769">your</span> <span begin="00:53.769" end="00:54.579">e</span><span begin="00:54.579" end="00:54.819">ne</span><span begin="00:54.819" end="00:55.656">mi</span><span begin="00:55.656" end="00:56.051">es</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你背负着旧日的仇敌</span></p><p begin="00:56.609" end="01:00.014" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:56.609" end="00:56.739">But</span> <span begin="00:56.739" end="00:56.994">they're</span> <span begin="00:56.994" end="00:57.504">so</span> <span begin="00:57.504" end="00:58.079">fa</span><span begin="00:58.079" end="00:58.869">mi</span><span begin="00:58.869" end="01:00.014">liar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">却认不出熟悉的轮廓</span></p><p begin="01:01.034" end="01:04.488" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="01:01.034" end="01:01.274">I'm</span> <span begin="01:01.274" end="01:01.738">sick</span> <span begin="01:01.738" end="01:02.173">of</span> <span begin="01:02.173" end="01:02.316">the</span> <span begin="01:02.316" end="01:03.151">com</span><span begin="01:03.151" end="01:03.448">pa</span><span begin="01:03.448" end="01:04.488">ny</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我已厌倦这冰冷的相伴</span></p><p begin="01:05.171" end="01:07.327" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="01:05.171" end="01:05.313">So</span> <span begin="01:05.313" end="01:05.553">I</span> <span begin="01:05.553" end="01:05.981">cull</span> <span begin="01:05.981" end="01:06.319">the</span> <span begin="01:06.319" end="01:07.327">shame</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">索性将羞耻尽数焚光</span></p><p begin="01:07.962" end="01:11.774" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="01:07.962" end="01:08.024">And</span> <span begin="01:08.024" end="01:08.247">I</span> <span begin="01:08.247" end="01:08.514">know</span> <span begin="01:08.514" end="01:08.755">you'll</span> <span begin="01:08.755" end="01:09.290">say</span> <span begin="01:09.290" end="01:09.917">how</span> <span begin="01:09.917" end="01:10.329">I'm</span> <span begin="01:10.329" end="01:10.594">a</span> <span begin="01:10.594" end="01:11.264">bur</span><span begin="01:11.264" end="01:11.774">den</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我知道你定会斥我如重担</span></p><p begin="01:12.187" end="01:15.932" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="01:12.187" end="01:12.529">Yeah,</span> <span begin="01:12.529" end="01:12.789">do</span> <span begin="01:12.789" end="01:13.062">your</span> <span begin="01:13.062" end="01:13.637">worst,</span> <span begin="01:13.637" end="01:14.667">all</span> <span begin="01:14.667" end="01:14.862">at</span> <span begin="01:14.862" end="01:15.932">once</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">来吧，任风霜一齐倾落</span></p><p begin="01:16.422" end="01:18.674" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="01:16.422" end="01:16.539">I</span> <span begin="01:16.539" end="01:16.797">know</span> <span begin="01:16.797" end="01:17.062">what</span> <span begin="01:17.062" end="01:17.372">you</span> <span begin="01:17.372" end="01:17.722">want</span> <span begin="01:17.722" end="01:18.092">from</span> <span begin="01:18.092" end="01:18.674">me</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:18.889" end="01:20.166"><span begin="01:18.889" end="01:19.317">(from</span> <span begin="01:19.317" end="01:20.166">me)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">自我心底</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我懂你索求的暗涌</span></p><p begin="01:20.702" end="01:22.757" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="01:20.702" end="01:20.817">I</span> <span begin="01:20.817" end="01:21.099">know</span> <span begin="01:21.099" end="01:21.367">what</span> <span begin="01:21.367" end="01:21.647">you're</span> <span begin="01:21.647" end="01:22.019">thin</span><span begin="01:22.019" end="01:22.757">king</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:22.610" end="01:24.919"><span begin="01:22.610" end="01:22.895">(thin</span><span begin="01:22.895" end="01:23.214">king,</span> <span begin="01:23.492" end="01:23.674">thin</span><span begin="01:23.674" end="01:24.034">king,</span> <span begin="01:24.234" end="01:24.432">thin</span><span begin="01:24.432" end="01:24.919">king)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">寻索，叩问，回响不息</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我听见你盘旋的思绪</span></p><p begin="01:25.022" end="01:29.122" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="01:25.022" end="01:25.145">And</span> <span begin="01:25.145" end="01:25.335">it's</span> <span begin="01:25.335" end="01:25.652">not</span> <span begin="01:25.652" end="01:25.912">the</span> <span begin="01:25.912" end="01:26.400">voice</span> <span begin="01:26.400" end="01:27.030">of</span> <span begin="01:27.030" end="01:27.497">all</span> <span begin="01:27.497" end="01:27.767">the</span> <span begin="01:27.767" end="01:28.362">o</span><span begin="01:28.362" end="01:29.122">thers</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那并非旁人的回音</span></p><p begin="01:29.395" end="01:32.980" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:29.395" end="01:29.707">You've</span> <span begin="01:29.707" end="01:29.985">on</span><span begin="01:29.985" end="01:30.197">ly</span> <span begin="01:30.197" end="01:30.785">said</span> <span begin="01:30.785" end="01:31.322">it</span> <span begin="01:31.322" end="01:31.725">to</span> <span begin="01:31.725" end="01:32.062">your</span><span begin="01:32.062" end="01:32.980">self</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你只在镜中对自己低语</span></p><p begin="01:33.590" end="01:35.792" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:33.590" end="01:33.715">I</span> <span begin="01:33.715" end="01:33.952">know</span> <span begin="01:33.952" end="01:34.237">what</span> <span begin="01:34.237" end="01:34.525">you</span> <span begin="01:34.525" end="01:34.855">want</span> <span begin="01:34.855" end="01:35.242">from</span> <span begin="01:35.242" end="01:35.792">me</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:36.057" end="01:37.235"><span begin="01:36.057" end="01:36.455">(from</span> <span begin="01:36.455" end="01:37.235">me)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">自我心底</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我懂你索求的暗涌</span></p><p begin="01:37.853" end="01:40.051" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:37.853" end="01:37.988">I</span> <span begin="01:37.988" end="01:38.233">know</span> <span begin="01:38.233" end="01:38.483">what</span> <span begin="01:38.483" end="01:38.786">you're</span> <span begin="01:38.786" end="01:39.131">thin</span><span begin="01:39.131" end="01:40.051">king</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:39.681" end="01:42.749"><span begin="01:39.681" end="01:39.848">(They</span> <span begin="01:39.848" end="01:40.031">come</span> <span begin="01:40.031" end="01:40.211">to</span> <span begin="01:40.211" end="01:40.428">feel</span> <span begin="01:40.428" end="01:40.646">like</span> <span begin="01:40.646" end="01:41.084">things</span> <span begin="01:41.084" end="01:41.317">we're</span> <span begin="01:41.317" end="01:41.567">say</span><span begin="01:41.567" end="01:41.772">ing</span> <span begin="01:41.772" end="01:41.934">to</span> <span begin="01:41.934" end="01:42.077">our</span><span begin="01:42.077" end="01:42.749">selves)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">渐渐化作，我们对自己的独白</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我听见你盘旋的思绪</span></p><p begin="01:43.884" end="01:47.668" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:43.884" end="01:43.986">It's</span> <span begin="01:43.986" end="01:44.113">an</span> <span begin="01:44.113" end="01:44.556">inch</span> <span begin="01:44.556" end="01:44.916">from</span> <span begin="01:44.916" end="01:45.221">my</span> <span begin="01:45.221" end="01:46.011">ears</span> <span begin="01:46.011" end="01:46.238">a</span><span begin="01:46.238" end="01:47.668">gain</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">耳畔又贴着一寸寒霜</span></p><p begin="01:48.138" end="01:51.748" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:48.138" end="01:48.331">You</span> <span begin="01:48.331" end="01:48.876">should</span> <span begin="01:48.876" end="01:49.436">be</span> <span begin="01:49.436" end="01:50.376">sor</span><span begin="01:50.376" end="01:51.748">ry</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你该感到抱歉</span></p><p begin="01:52.426" end="01:54.301" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:52.426" end="01:52.663">A</span> <span begin="01:52.663" end="01:53.036">so</span><span begin="01:53.036" end="01:53.463">lemn</span> <span begin="01:53.463" end="01:54.301">man</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">做个沉静的模样</span></p><p begin="01:54.573" end="01:59.893" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:54.573" end="01:54.821">A</span> <span begin="01:54.821" end="01:55.263">bet</span><span begin="01:55.263" end="01:55.588">ter</span> <span begin="01:55.588" end="01:56.520">song</span> <span begin="01:56.736" end="01:56.968">to</span> <span begin="01:56.968" end="01:57.503">fix</span> <span begin="01:57.503" end="01:58.036">my</span> <span begin=